Class Administrator

java.lang.Object
Shared.Users
Shared.Staff
Administrator.Administrator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Administrator extends Staff
Administrator class are for users who have administrative privileges in the HMS system. Administrator class extends the Staff class and inherits properties from the Staff class(password,email,phone number,gender,date of birth and age)
Author:
Maestro, Johnson Chow, Cheng Jun Long Brandon
